---
export const prerender = true;
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Atelier Néra — Ébéniste sur mesure · Drôme</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Atelier Néra, ébéniste artisan haut de gamme spécialisé dans le mobilier sur mesure et les cuisines artisanales dans la Drôme." />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link rel="preload" as="style" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" media="print" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" id="gfonts-nera" />
  <noscript><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" /></noscript>
  <script>var l=document.getElementById('gfonts-nera');if(l)l.onload=function(){l.media='all'};</script>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --cream: #F5F0E8;
      --cream-dark: #EBE4D8;
      --dark: #1E1810;
      --brown: #7A5C3E;
      --gold: #B8862E;
      --mid: rgba(30,24,16,0.55);
      --font: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: var(--font); background: var(--cream); color: var(--dark); overflow-x: hidden; }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding: 1.6rem 5rem;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }
    nav.scrolled {
      background: rgba(245,240,232,0.97);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      padding: 1rem 5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(30,24,16,0.08);
    }
    .nav-logo { font-family: var(--font); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: #F5F0E8; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.4s; }
    nav.scrolled .nav-logo { color: var(--dark); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.7); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s; }
    nav.scrolled .nav-links a { color: var(--mid); }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold) !important; }
    .nav-cta {
      font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--cream); border: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.35); padding: 0.55rem 1.4rem;
      text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s; border-radius: 2px;
    }
    nav.scrolled .nav-cta { color: var(--dark); border-color: rgba(30,24,16,0.25); }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold); color: #fff !important; }

    /* NOTICE FICTIF */
    .notice-fictif {
      position: fixed; bottom: 1.5rem; right: 1.5rem; z-index: 999;
      background: var(--dark); color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55);
      padding: 0.75rem 1.1rem; font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 400;
      max-width: 250px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;
      border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
    }
    .notice-fictif strong { color: var(--gold); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 600; }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: flex-end;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: var(--dark);
      padding: 0 5rem 7rem;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566041510639-8d95a2490bfb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
      opacity: 0.38;
    }
    .hero-gradient { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(30,24,16,0.96) 0%, rgba(30,24,16,0.28) 60%, transparent 100%); }
    .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 720px; }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow::before { content: ''; display: block; width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--font); font-weight: 600;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5.5vw, 5rem); line-height: 1.08;
      color: var(--cream); letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }
    .hero h1 span { color: var(--gold); }
    .hero-sub { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.52); max-width: 420px; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-hero {
      font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--cream); text-decoration: none;
      background: rgba(245,240,232,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.25);
      padding: 0.85rem 2rem; border-radius: 2px;
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .btn-hero:hover { background: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold); }
    .btn-hero-ghost {
      font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55); text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .btn-hero-ghost:hover { color: var(--cream); }

    /* SECTION LABEL */
    .section-label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem; }

    /* ABOUT */
    .about { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr; gap: 6rem; align-items: center; padding: 8rem 5rem; }
    .about-img-wrap { aspect-ratio: 3/4; overflow: hidden; }
    .about-img-wrap img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transition: transform 0.9s ease; }
    .about-img-wrap:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
    .about-stat-row { display: flex; gap: 3rem; margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 2.5rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(30,24,16,0.1); }
    .stat-num { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--dark); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
    .stat-lbl { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--mid); }
    .about h2 { font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 600; color: var(--dark); line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 1.8rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .about p { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.85; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }

    /* SAVOIR-FAIRE */
    .savoir-faire { background: var(--dark); padding: 8rem 5rem; }
    .savoir-faire .section-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; margin-bottom: 4.5rem; gap: 3rem; }
    .savoir-faire h2 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.2rem); font-weight: 600; color: var(--cream); line-height: 1.1; max-width: 480px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .savoir-faire-sub { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.38); max-width: 240px; text-align: right; }
    .sf-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(245,240,232,0.06); }
    .sf-card { background: var(--dark); padding: 3rem 2.5rem; transition: background 0.4s; }
    .sf-card:hover { background: rgba(245,240,232,0.04); }
    .sf-num { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(184,134,46,0.18); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .sf-card h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .sf-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.8; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.42); }
    .sf-tag { display: inline-block; margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gold); }

    /* GALERIE */
    .galerie { padding: 8rem 5rem; }
    .galerie-intro { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }
    .galerie h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 2.8vw, 2.6rem); font-weight: 600; color: var(--dark); line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .galerie-link { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
    .galerie-link:hover { opacity: 0.7; }
    .galerie-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 280px 280px;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .g-item { overflow: hidden; position: relative; cursor: pointer; background: var(--cream-dark); }
    .g-item:nth-child(1) { grid-row: span 2; }
    .g-item:nth-child(5) { grid-column: span 2; }
    .g-item img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; transition: transform 0.8s ease; }
    .g-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: rgba(30,24,16,0); transition: background 0.4s; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .g-overlay span { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--cream); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.4s; }
    .g-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.06); }
    .g-item:hover .g-overlay { background: rgba(30,24,16,0.55); }
    .g-item:hover .g-overlay span { opacity: 1; }

    /* PROCESSUS */
    .processus { background: var(--cream-dark); padding: 8rem 5rem; }
    .processus h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 2.8vw, 2.6rem); font-weight: 600; color: var(--dark); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 5rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .process-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 2rem; }
    .p-step { text-align: center; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
    .p-num {
      width: 3.5rem; height: 3.5rem; border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(184,134,46,0.3); margin: 0 auto 2rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gold);
      transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    }
    .p-step:hover .p-num { border-color: var(--gold); background: rgba(184,134,46,0.08); }
    .p-step h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
    .p-step p { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--mid); }

    /* TEMOIGNAGES */
    .temoignages { background: var(--dark); padding: 8rem 5rem; }
    .temoignages .section-label { color: var(--gold); }
    .temoignages h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 2.8vw, 2.6rem); font-weight: 600; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 4rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .temoignages-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(245,240,232,0.06); }
    .temoignage { background: var(--dark); padding: 2.5rem; transition: background 0.35s; }
    .temoignage:hover { background: rgba(245,240,232,0.04); }
    .t-stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .temoignage blockquote { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.75); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .t-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; }
    .t-avatar { width: 2.4rem; height: 2.4rem; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--brown); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--cream); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .t-name { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 500; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5); }
    .t-project { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--gold); margin-top: 0.2rem; }

    /* CONTACT */
    .contact { padding: 8rem 5rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr; gap: 8rem; align-items: start; }
    .contact-info h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 2.8vw, 2.6rem); font-weight: 600; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .contact-info p { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .contact-detail { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .c-label { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gold); min-width: 75px; padding-top: 1px; }
    .c-value { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--mid); }
    .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 1.8rem; }
    .form-group label { display: block; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
    .form-group input, .form-group textarea, .form-group select {
      width: 100%; background: transparent; border: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30,24,16,0.15); padding: 0.75rem 0;
      font-family: var(--font); font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--dark);
      transition: border-color 0.3s; outline: none;
    }
    .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus { border-color: var(--gold); }
    .form-group textarea { resize: none; height: 90px; }
    .btn-submit {
      background: var(--dark); color: var(--cream); border: none;
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem; font-family: var(--font);
      font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.3s; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    .btn-submit:hover { background: var(--gold); }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer { background: var(--dark); border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.07); }
    .footer-top { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; padding: 5rem 5rem 4rem; }
    .footer-brand-name { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--cream); letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .footer-brand-desc { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.32); max-width: 260px; }
    .footer-col h4 { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .footer-col ul { list-style: none; }
    .footer-col li { margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
    .footer-col a { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.38); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s; }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--cream); }
    .footer-bottom { padding: 1.5rem 5rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.06); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .footer-copy { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.22); }
    .footer-fictif { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.18); text-align: center; }
    .footer-caelestis { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.22); text-align: right; }
    .footer-caelestis a { color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; }

    /* REVEAL */
    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease; }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .reveal[data-d="1"] { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
    .reveal[data-d="2"] { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
    .reveal[data-d="3"] { transition-delay: 0.3s; }

    /* SCREEN-READER ONLY */
    .sr-only { position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: -1px; overflow: hidden; clip: rect(0,0,0,0); white-space: nowrap; border: 0; }

    /* SKIP LINK */
    .skip-link { position: absolute; left: -9999px; top: auto; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden; background: var(--gold); color: var(--dark); padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; z-index: 9999; text-decoration: none; }
    .skip-link:focus { left: 1rem; top: 1rem; width: auto; height: auto; overflow: visible; outline: 2px solid var(--dark); outline-offset: 2px; }

    /* PREFERS-REDUCED-MOTION */
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .reveal { opacity: 1 !important; transform: none !important; transition: none !important; }
      .about-img-wrap img, .g-item img, .bestseller-img img { transition: none !important; }
      .hero-bg { animation: none !important; }
    }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      nav { padding: 1.3rem 2.5rem; }
      nav.scrolled { padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem; }
      .hero { padding: 0 2.5rem 5rem; }
      .about, .contact { padding: 6rem 2.5rem; gap: 3.5rem; }
      .savoir-faire, .galerie, .processus, .temoignages { padding: 6rem 2.5rem; }
      .footer-top { padding: 4rem 2.5rem 3rem; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .footer-bottom { padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links, .nav-cta { display: none; }
      .about, .contact { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .sf-grid, .temoignages-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .process-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .galerie-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; grid-template-rows: auto; }
      .g-item:nth-child(1), .g-item:nth-child(5) { grid-row: span 1; grid-column: span 1; }
      .galerie-intro, .savoir-faire .section-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.8rem; }
      .savoir-faire-sub { text-align: left; }
      .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
      .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
      .about-stat-row { gap: 2rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Aller au contenu principal</a>

  <!-- NOTICE FICTIF -->
  <div class="notice-fictif">
    <strong>Projet fictif</strong>
    Démonstration des possibilités offertes par <a href="https://caelestis.fr" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none;">Caelestis</a>
  </div>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav id="navbar" aria-label="Navigation principale">
    <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Atelier Néra</a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#savoir-faire">Savoir-faire</a></li>
      <li><a href="#galerie">Réalisations</a></li>
      <li><a href="#processus">Processus</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Demander un devis</a>
  </nav>

  <main id="main-content" tabindex="-1">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-gradient"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">Ébéniste artisan · Drôme, France</div>
      <h1>L'art du bois.<br><span>Le soin du détail.</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Chaque pièce est pensée, dessinée et construite à la main. Du mobilier sur mesure qui raconte votre histoire et dure toute une vie.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#galerie" class="btn-hero">Voir les réalisations →</a>
        <a href="#processus" class="btn-hero-ghost">Comment ça marche</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="about">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="about-img-wrap">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585771724684-38269d6639fd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Mathieu Néra, ébéniste artisan dans son atelier" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="section-label reveal">L'artisan</p>
      <h2 class="reveal" data-d="1">Mathieu Néra,<br>façonneur de bois depuis 2006.</h2>
      <p class="reveal" data-d="1">Né dans une famille d'artisans de la Drôme, j'ai appris le bois avant les mots. Ce métier n'est pas une vocation tardive, c'est une évidence transmise de génération en génération.</p>
      <p class="reveal" data-d="2">Chaque pièce que je crée est le résultat d'un dialogue : avec le client qui imagine, avec le bois qui dicte ses contraintes, et avec l'espace qui accueillera l'objet. Je ne produis pas du mobilier, je construis des présences.</p>
      <p class="reveal" data-d="2">Essences locales, finitions à la cire naturelle, quincaillerie sur mesure. Rien n'est laissé au hasard.</p>
      <div class="about-stat-row reveal" data-d="3">
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num">340+</div>
          <div class="stat-lbl">Pièces créées</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num">100%</div>
          <div class="stat-lbl">Sur mesure</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num">12</div>
          <div class="stat-lbl">Essences travaillées</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SAVOIR-FAIRE -->
  <section class="savoir-faire" id="savoir-faire">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <h2>Trois disciplines,<br>une seule exigence.</h2>
      <p class="savoir-faire-sub">Du mobilier à la cuisine, chaque réalisation est l'expression d'un savoir-faire rare, transmis et perfectionné.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sf-grid">
      <div class="sf-card reveal">
        <div class="sf-num">01</div>
        <h3>Mobilier sur mesure</h3>
